reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 26, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Great quality, clear instructions, easy to put together. Wish I’d gotten one a little bit bigger but it’s still a very good size for my original intentions. Great for my daughter to use for her iPad and drawing or watching something on my laptop. I bought her one of those crayola art cases to use for her drawing and just didn’t think about 1) how big the case was or 2) how obsessed with it she would be and how she wouldn’t want to transfer the crayons, markers, and colored pencils to another more size appropriate case to use with her desk haha. The desk just isn’t big enough to comfortably have the case open while drawing. That’s not the desk’s fault and is entirely mine. Just a warning to maybe go bigger than you think you need.
